(Pre-compiled versions of the manual can be found in the Documentation section
of the Siesta web page (https://icmab.es/siesta).

To prepare a hard-copy version of the manual, use the (pdf)LaTeX program:

Formerly, one had to do manually:

pdflatex siesta
pdflatex siesta
splitidx siesta
makeindex siesta
pdflatex siesta
pdflatex siesta

Type 'make final' to fully create the manual.
Type 'make' if you do not have 'splitidx' and/or 'makeindex'.


